    R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    collapse (>= 2.0.0)
Suggests:
    bench,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    vctrs
LinkingTo: 
    cpp11
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Encoding: UTF-8
